commit 42d03a0e3b0e5eaa4b8169a126c2f76cc9b447e7
Author: Raffaele De Feo <alberthilbert@gmail.com>
Date:   Wed Oct 17 18:54:11 2018 +0200

    Add a widget to the pdf viewer toolbar to show and set the current
    page number.
---
